---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Individual Health & Dental Plans | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Individual health and dental plans for self-employed, retired, or Canadians without group benefits — Heidi Blondin Financial, Kingston ON."
>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-brand-plum mb-6 text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Individual Health Plans and Dental Plans</h1>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-5" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Don't have Employee Benefits through your Employer?</h2>

      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-5">
        <p>Heidi Blondin Financial offers a wide range of Individual Health Packages and Dental Plans to choose from. Whether you're self-employed, between jobs or retired, there is a perfect health care package of benefits available for you and your family. With the ongoing changes to provincial health care plans, it is important to ensure you have affordable protection against unexpected medical expenses. The Individual Health Plans offer an excellent range of supplementary health and dental benefits, including prescription drugs, vision and hospital.</p>
        <p>The premiums for your individual health plan are eligible medical expenses under the Canadian Federal Income Tax Act.</p>
        <p>You can review various plan options and pricing <a href="/financial-services/insurance-quote/" class="text-brand-gold underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-amber-700">here</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6">
        <a href="/financial-services/insurance-quote/" class="btn-ghost">Options &amp; Pricing</a>
      </div>

      <p class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed mt-4">Contact Heidi Blondin directly for additional plan options.</p>

      <div class="mt-12 bg-brand-tintPlum p-8">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-4" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Are you leaving your Employer?</h2>
        <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
          <p>You can continue to receive coverage similar to the employee health benefits and dental plans you have today. Heidi Blondin Financial offers several group benefit plan conversion options from your existing group plan.</p>
          <p><strong>Don't wait – <a href="/financial-services/insurance-quote/" class="text-brand-gold underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-amber-700">Apply now</a>!</strong> The conversion of your Health Plan needs to be completed in the first 60 days after you leave your employer.</p>
          <p>Contact us today for further details. Or visit to select the right plan for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-brand-tintPlum">
        <blockquote class="quote-mark">
          <p class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed italic">My partner and I have worked with Heidi Blondin of Blondin Financial for almost a year. We recently retired and needed help with our financial planning and investments. We needed sound, honest and prudent advice. First and foremost was to find someone that we could trust, feel comfortable and confident with and who understood our personal needs and desires. This is Heidi. More than thrilled to have found someone that meets all of our requirements and more. We honestly feel so fortunate to have found her.</p>
          <footer class="font-sans text-sm font-medium text-brand-plum mt-3">P.M. – Kingston, Ontario</footer>
        </blockquote>
        <p class="mt-6"><a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Heidi+Blondin+Financial/@44.2602899,-76.5399038,17z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0x4cd2ab2e0b9dc5f3:0xf4fc562e5c6d96cc!8m2!3d44.2602899!4d-76.5377151!9m1!1b1" class="font-sans text-sm font-medium text-brand-gold underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-amber-700" target="_blank" rel="noopener">See &amp; Write Reviews for Heidi</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand />

</BaseLayout>
